text: Soso Tamarau (born 16 May 1984) is a Nigerian freestyle wrestler. At the 2016 Summer Olympics he competed in the Men’s freestyle -97 kg. ==References== Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic wrestlers of Nigeria Category:Wrestlers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Nigeria Category:Wrestlers at the 2014 Commonwealth Games Category:African Games gold medalists for Nigeria Category:African Games silver medalists for Nigeria Category:African Games medalists in wrestling Category:Competitors at the 2015 African Games Category:Competitors at the 2019 African Games
